CBRE & Colliers are pleased to present Lot 2 of 12 Distribution Court, Arundel to the market for lease. This exciting new development is the second stage of the multi – warehouse development by Logos. 
The development will include 8 warehouses ranging from 1,396sqm through to 7,304sqm which will be available to occupy in Q2 2022.

12 Distribution Court 
Unit 1 - 2,079 sqm - Available
Unit 2 – 1,886 sqm - Available
Unit 3 – 1,886 sqm - Available
Unit 4 – 1,453 sqm - Available 
Unit 5 – 1,851 sqm - Available
Unit 6 - 1,396 sqm - Available
Unit 7 - 1,396 sqm - Available
Unit 8 - 1,818 sqm - LEASED

Property Features Include:
- 10.5-meter-high sprinklered warehouses (allowing for up to 6 pallet heigh storage)
- Container high roller doors
- Access to 3 phase power
- 5 Star Green Star Design & Construction
- 20kw Solar System per tenancy
- Dedicated hardstands per tenancy
- Easy access for large vehicles
- All weather awnings for loading and unloading
- High quality office facilities

Call one of our exclusive agents if you would like to know more information about this exciting opportunity.

CBRE are pleased to present 5 Wrights Place, Arundel for lease. 

The property is located on the corner Brisbane Road and Wrights Place which provides business with excellent exposure to Brisbane Road. 

The property features: 

-	1,000sqm of office / warehouse 
-	3,222sqm of land area 
-	Access to 3 phase power 
-	Drive through capability 
-	Wash bay 
-	2 street access 
-	Large concrete apron and hardstand 

For further information on this outstanding opportunity contact your exclusive agents.

CBRE are pleased to present Arundel's newest industrial unit opportunity at Lot 7 Logistics Place. 

This exciting new development will feature the following: 

- 7 high quality industrial units 
- Unit sizes range from 200sqm – 349/sqm 
- Pricing from $549,000 - $989,000 + GST 
- Excellent office / showroom finishes 
- High clearance warehouses with electric roller door 
- Constructed from concrete tilt panel
- Corner location with good street frontage 
- Zoned medium impact business
- Units are available for sale and lease. 

For further information on this exciting new development please contact CBRE today.
